<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
<style>

    body {
        margin: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .header .name {
        font-size: 25px;
        font-family: 'Sriracha', cursive;
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin-left: 30px;
    }

    .nav-items {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        margin-right: 20px;
    }

    .nav-items a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #000;
        padding: 35px 20px;
    }

    .logo {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        width: 100%;
        height: 520px;
        background: url("/images/HomeImage.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

    .features {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 40px 80px;
    }

    .features .feature {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .features .feature .feature-heading {
        font-size: 20px;
        color: #333333;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .features .feature .feature-text {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #585858;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .rules {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 40px 80px;
        border-top: 2px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .rules h2 {
        font-size: 30px;
        color: #333333;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .rules-text p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #585858;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .footer {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        background: url("/images/FooterImage.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="header">
    <a  class="name">Leonardo</a>
    <nav class="nav-items">
        <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Home")">Home</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Login", "Account")">Login</a>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Register", "Account")">Register</a>
    </nav>
</header>

 <main>

    <div class="logo"></div>

    <div class="features">

        <div class="feature">
            <p class="feature-heading">Paint</p>
            <p class="feature-text">Convince your friends that you are the next Leonardo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <p class="feature-heading">Guess</p>
            <p class="feature-text">Guess what they are drawing and increase your score.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <p class="feature-heading">Chat</p>
            <p class="feature-text">Exchange messages during the game. Give each other tips, share your thoughts.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="rules">
        <div class="rules-text">
            <h2>Game rules:</h2>
            <p>The painter tries to draw the given word or phrase, which the other players try to guess. If the painter thinks there is nothing more they can do to help the others guess what they have drawn, they have the option of passing the drawing role to the next player. Each right guess is worth one point, the player with the most points wins the game.</p>
            <p>Have fun!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</main>

    <footer class="footer">
    <div class="copy">&copy; 2022 sd.Auth.Web</div>
    </footer>

</body>